---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Prusa | 3D3D"
  description="Thinking about a Prusa? Talk to me first. I've run them from the MK2 forward and know exactly what to get for your setup."
  activePath="/prusa"
>
  <section class="prusa-page">
    <div class="prusa-shell">
      <p class="prusa-eyebrow">Prusa Equipment</p>
      <h1 class="prusa-title">
        Thinking about<br />a Prusa?
      </h1>
      <p class="prusa-body">
        I've run Prusa from the MK2 forward. I know the lineup, the use cases, and what actually makes sense for your setup. Before you buy, talk to me.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="prusa-cta">Talk to me →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="prusa-story">
    <div class="prusa-story__shell">
      <p class="prusa-story__eyebrow">Sponsorship</p>
      <h2 class="prusa-story__title">Prusa believes in 3D3D.</h2>
      <p class="prusa-story__body">
        Prusa is sponsoring 3D3D with a CORE One L. Not as a marketing deal, but because they saw the work and backed the mission. A founder-operated fabrication operation taking 3D printing offshore, to events, to communities. They believe in the dream, and so do I.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="prusa-cta">Talk to me →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prusa-page {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: #111214;
    color: #F6F7FA;
  }

  .prusa-shell {
    width: min(100% - clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem), 720px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.6rem;
    padding-block: clamp(6rem, 10vw, 10rem);
  }

  .prusa-eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-tech);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #40C4C4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .prusa-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 2.75rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: #40C4C4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prusa-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 2rem + 4vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .prusa-body {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 36rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 0.95rem + 0.4vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(246, 247, 250, 0.82);
  }

  .prusa-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: fit-content;
    min-height: 3.4rem;
    padding: 0.95rem 1.6rem;
    background: #40C4C4;
    color: #0F1112;
    border: 3px solid #1A1A1A;
    font-family: var(--font-tech);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: background-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(64, 196, 196, 0.22);
  }

  .prusa-cta:hover {
    background: #53D3D3;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(64, 196, 196, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .prusa-story {
    background: #0F1112;
    color: #F6F7FA;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(64, 196, 196, 0.15);
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
  }

  .prusa-story__shell {
    width: min(100% - clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem), 720px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .prusa-story__eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-tech);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #40C4C4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .prusa-story__eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 2.75rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: #40C4C4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prusa-story__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.2rem + 2.5vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .prusa-story__body {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 36rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 0.95rem + 0.4vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(246, 247, 250, 0.82);
  }
</style>
